data.title: STA: Drnovsek Meets Solana and Saxe
data.meta_description: Slovenian President Janez Drnovsek discussed current European topics with High Representative for CFSP Javier Solana and separately with Bulgarian Prime Minister Simeon Saxe-Coburg Gotha on the sideline of the Davos World Economic Forum. The Bulgarian PM also expressed a wish to visit Slovenia, said the president's office.
data.text:
Davos, 24 January - Slovenian President Janez Drnovsek discussed current European topics with High Representative for CFSP Javier Solana and separately with Bulgarian Prime Minister Simeon Saxe-Coburg Gotha on the sideline of the Davos World Economic Forum. The Bulgarian PM also expressed a wish to visit Slovenia, said the president's office.
